        "description": {
            "value": "<p>You are an able medic, allowing you to mend wounds quickly and get your allies back in the fight. You gain the following benefits:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Increase your Intelligence or Wisdom score by 1, to a maximum of 20.</li>\n<li>When you use a traumakit to stabilize a dying creature, that creature also regains 1 hit point.</li>\n<li>As an action, you can spend one use of a traumakit to tend to a creature and restore 1d6 + 4 hit points to it, plus additional hit points equal to the creature's maximum number of Hit Dice. The creature can't regain hit points again in this way until it finishes a short or long rest.</li>\n</ul>",
